partnerDetails.about:
OSCAR - EL specialized in the field of design, production of electrical boards, engineering, electrical control and automation, systems for process control, construction and assembly works, warranty and after-sales service of equipment for production process management.

SERVICES and SOLUTIONS :

  • ENGINEERING - From concept to start up and setup
  • TABLE MANUFACTURING - design and manufacture of electrical panels for power supply, control and automation of various technological processes in industrial sites.
  • AUTOMATION – SCADA, PLC
  • ELECTRICAL - range of services related to the construction of electrical installations of buildings and facilities.
  • INSTALLATION – Form concept to start up and set up
